on during Spring context initialization\n   (DefaultSystemService.afterPropertiesSet). If the revision is missing\n   or blank, throw IllegalStateException to abort context startup.\n\n2. In the embedded Tomcat entry point (Main.java), catch all startup\n   failure paths and call System.exit(1):\n   - tomcat.start() failure (e.g. port in use)\n   - Spring context init failure (caught via TomcatStarter.startUpException\n     which was previously stored but never checked)\n   - Deferred servlet load failure (previously killed the await thread\n     silently)\n\nOnly affects the embedded server (java -jar dhis.war). WAR deployments\nto external servlet containers are not impacted since Main is never\ninvoked in that scenario.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"17573fa6dd7061c970784167e6dd7e9b2875ab3f","tree_id":"0a85a55d62b36451792fb0a8e8b82b378f486951","timestamp":"2026-03-13T19:22:54Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"ht